19:["$","p",null,{"className":"mb-5","children":"This website may contain links to external websites that are not provided or maintained by or in any way affiliated with KFLR. Please note that KFLR does not guarantee the accuracy, relevance, timeliness, or completeness of any information on these external websites. We have no control over the nature, content, and availability of those sites. The inclusion of any links does not necessarily imply a recommendation or endorse the views expressed within them. Your use of external websites is subject to their respective terms of use and privacy policies."}]
