1b:["$","p",null,{"className":"mb-4","children":"KFLR reserves the right to modify, suspend, or discontinue any portion of this website or our services at any time without notice. We also reserve the right to change prices, product offerings, specifications, and availability of products and services without prior notice."}]
1c:["$","p",null,{"className":"mb-5","children":"While we will make reasonable efforts to notify existing customers of significant changes to contracted services, we are not liable for any modifications, price changes, suspensions, or discontinuance of services. Service level agreements (SLAs) and support commitments apply only to active contracts and are subject to the specific terms outlined in your service agreement."}]
1d:["$","h4",null,{"id":"compliance","className":"mb-3","children":"Compliance and Regulatory Responsibility"}]
1e:["$","p",null,{"className":"mb-4","children":"While KFLR can assist with implementing security controls and technical measures to support compliance with various regulations (such as PDPA, ISO 27001, PCI-DSS), the ultimate responsibility for regulatory compliance rests with your organization."}]
1f:["$","p",null,{"className":"mb-5","children":"We are not legal advisors and cannot provide legal interpretations of regulatory requirements. Organizations subject to specific compliance mandates should engage qualified legal counsel and compliance specialists to ensure all regulatory obligations are met. KFLR's role is limited to implementing technical controls and providing documentation to support your compliance efforts."}]
20:["$","h4",null,{"id":"testimonials","className":"mb-3","children":"Testimonials and Case Studies"}]
21:["$","p",null,{"className":"mb-5","children":"Testimonials and case studies presented on this website represent the experiences and opinions of individual clients. They are not necessarily representative of what others may achieve. Results may vary and are not guaranteed. Project timelines, cost savings, performance improvements, and other outcomes described in case studies are specific to those engagements and may not be replicated in different environments or circumstances."}]
